Effectiveness ratings are determined by the following criteria: 
- 'Highly Effective': Average interaction rating greater than 4 and at least one closed sale; 
- 'Moderately Effective': Average interaction rating greater than 3 and at least one closed sale; 
- 'Less Effective': Failing to meet the above criteria.

